{"lemma":"تَشَدُّد","slug":"تَشَدُّد","root":"ش.د.د","root_slug":"ش-د-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-د-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21910"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%B4%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%8F%D9%91%D8%AF"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be strict, harsh, severe"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become extremist, to adopt extreme or radical views"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of تَشَدَّدَ (tašaddada) (form V)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"strictness, severity, harshness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"extremism, radicalism"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ta.ʃad.da.da/","/ta.ʃad.dud/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21910","headword_ar":"تشدّد","root":"$d","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He acted, or behaved, with forced hardness, firmness, strength, vigour, hardiness, courage, vehemence, severity, strictness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rigour; he exerted his strength, force,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"energy; strained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strained himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tasked himself severely;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSal~aba","text_ar":"تَصَلَّبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Slb","text_ar":"صلب"},{"kind":"text","text":";) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahada","text_ar":"جَهَدَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafosahu","text_ar":"نَفْسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (L;) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Al$~aYo'i","text_ar":"فِى الشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi","text_ar":"فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAd~a","text_ar":"شَادَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almu$aAd~apu fiY Al$~aYo'i","text_ar":"المُشَادَّةُ فِى الشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~a$ad~udu fiyhi","text_ar":"التَّشَدُّدُ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify the same: (S, L, K: * [see an ex. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t$d~d","text_ar":"تشدّد"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the first paragraph of art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jld","text_ar":"جلد"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) [and] both of these phrases signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the showing hardness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(PS.) You say also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t$d~d liloA^amori","text_ar":"تشدّد لِلْاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He applied himself with hardness, firmness, vigour, hardiness, severity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rigour, to the affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$ad~adati Alqayonapu","text_ar":"تَشَدَّدَتِ القَيْنَةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The slavesongstress strained herself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tasked herself severely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in raising her voice in singing. (L.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficult:"},{"kind":"text","text":"you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saA^alonaA fulaAnFA HaAjapF fata$ad~ada EalayonaA","text_ar":"سَاَلْنَا فُلَانًا حَاجَةً فَتَشَدَّدَ عَلَيْنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We asked of such a one a thing wanted, and he was hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficult, to us"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wEr","text_ar":"وعر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, niggardly, tenacious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"avaricious."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, KL.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}